Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:06.82,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:15.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:27.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:34.79,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In a certain world,\Nwhere magic is everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:39.49,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and Yuno were abandoned \Non the same day at
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:42.44,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,a church in the village of Hage, \Nwhich lies in the boonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:46.74,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They both dreamed of becoming the Wizard \NKing, the highest rank among mages,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:49.67,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and worked hard every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.09,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In the year they turned fifteen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:57.51,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,they both received grimoires,\Nwhich enhance the owner's magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.88,0:01:00.64,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They then took the Magic Knights \NEntrance Exam to join
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:03.35,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the Magic Knights, which are \Nled by the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.72,0:01:09.06,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see who can become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.87,0:01:14.53,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, because Yuno possesses \Nimmense magical powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:18.20,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,out of the nine squads, he chose \Nthe elite Golden Dawn to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:20.41,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,As for Asta, who had no magical powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:24.12,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,he ended up joining the squad \Nof rogues, the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.79,0:01:28.96,main,ASta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still going to become \Nthe Wizard King someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:38.61,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Thus the two finally took the first step \Ntoward becoming the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:57.28,main,Farmer,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:19.11,main,Farmer,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:34.50,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, there's trouble. An anomaly—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:36.19,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,An anomaly has occurred, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:43.76,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Let's have them work on this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:45.43,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:07.95,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:12.15,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And cower at reality
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:16.91,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:21.37,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of just making excuses to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:22.24,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:23.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:24.49,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:28.08,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:28.08,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(The decisive battle is still a long way off)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:30.24,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:36.13,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:39.30,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And get the world on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:42.97,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the reason I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:48.30,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time somewhere under this sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:54.32,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the tearful nights
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:57.61,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And head where the light shines
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:04:01.44,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my promise
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:04.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:08.96,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,shape of love
