Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:22.96,sign_6302_46_Black_Bulls__Bas,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Black Bulls' Base
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:26.98,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Magna. Let's fight. No holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.25,top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred eighty-two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:29.19,top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred eighty-three...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:29.97,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,No way, you battle-obsessed freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:31.79,top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred eighty-four...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.97,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:34.21,top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred eighty-five...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:35.20,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna eat your pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.87,top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred eighty-six...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.60,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, I'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:40.03,top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred eighty-seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:38.55,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Will you fight me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:39.48,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:41.28,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:42.03,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred eighty-eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.63,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:45.19,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred eighty-nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:45.19,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Silvantus Schnauzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:47.56,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred ninety...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:48.03,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I think something else would be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:49.99,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred ninety-one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:52.34,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Like "Wine"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:52.54,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred ninety-two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:55.51,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred ninety-three...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:53.79,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:58.24,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred ninety-four...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:59.91,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I will allow you to borrow a single letter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:01.35,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred ninety-five...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:02.18,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,from the name of my little sister,\Nthe goddess Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:04.07,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred ninety-six...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:05.72,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I will let you take the "M." Be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.58,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred ninety-seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:08.67,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Make it something cooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:10.34,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred ninety-eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.34,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Like, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:12.32,top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine hundred ninety-nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.06,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Magnam Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:14.06,top,,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:15.81,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:17.52,top,,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand and one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:18.15,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You have no taste, Lady Noe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.06,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,More like {\i1}you{\i0} don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:20.21,top,,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand and two...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.85,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking of names looks like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.67,top,,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand and three...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:26.71,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I thought of one, too. I wonder if \Nthey'll ask. I think it's a good name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.71,top,,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand and four...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:28.88,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.88,top,,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand and five...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:33.08,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Can I fatten that bird up? \NHe looks really yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:31.51,top,,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand and six...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.08,top,,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand and seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.50,top,,0000,0000,0000,,One thousand and eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:36.96,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Does he lay eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:37.94,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:39.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely Toritaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:42.53,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's Silvantus Schnauzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Toritaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:47.49,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Silvantus Schnauzer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:48.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Toritaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:51.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:54.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The heck was that for, Toritaro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:55.54,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,There, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:06:00.36,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You prefer Silvantus Schnauzer, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:02.23,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:03.90,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Magnam Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:04.90,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,"M."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:06.03,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:11.07,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Why not Nero?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:12.74,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:14.40,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he approves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.04,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,"Nero" means "black."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.16,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Nero?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:25.12,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right, listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:27.95,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Yami! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:30.26,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,We're back, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:31.87,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:34.90,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What did they want at the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:40.10,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a mission, I want \Nto go with everyone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:42.71,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Mission? Is it a mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:47.07,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I have an announcement for you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:50.49,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,A new dungeon has been discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:54.21,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,A dungeon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:55.91,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious, Mister Yami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:59.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is a dungeon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:00.93,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:05.79,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious? You were surprised, \Nand you didn't even know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:07.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I just went with the flow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:09.01,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about predictable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.94,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. Dungeons are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:16.82,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of like ancient tombs that contain\Nrelics made by the people from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:19.30,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes they have info \Nabout powerful ancient magic
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.83,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,or super rare magical items.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:24.40,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,They're absolutely amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:27.29,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:32.40,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,The people back then set \Ninsane magical traps in them
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:35.22,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,so that they wouldn't get misused by anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:38.45,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,They're super dangerous and really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:44.77,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights always investigate them\Nsince they're so dangerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:47.71,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,and to make sure none of \Nthe treasures get stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.79,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:55.32,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the Black Bulls are \Nsupposed to investigate this
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,newly discovered dungeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:58.50,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:06.52,sign_11566_153_Clover_Kingdom,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(288,1)}Clover\NKingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:03.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Particularly because this dungeon \Npopped up near our enemy's border.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:06.52,sign_11639_155_Dungeon,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(211,1)}Dungeon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:04.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:06.52,sign_11713_157_Diamond__Kingdom,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(218,1)}Diamond\NKingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:06.52,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The Diamond Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:14.03,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We need to take care of this mission fast \Nso Diamond's people won't steal anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:18.76,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, there have been instances \Nin which someone found a magical item
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,that could change civilization\Nitself in a dungeon,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:24.26,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,and someone even learned how \Nto use the ultimate magic there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:27.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Me! Me! Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:30.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I might be able to use \Nthe ultimate magic, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:33.11,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any magic, \Nso that's not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:35.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You never know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:39.68,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you can go, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:43.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, the Wizard King chose you himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:47.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:50.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:52.85,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:56.10,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? Did you bump \Ninto the Wizard King somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No, never!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King chose me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:07.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Great Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:12.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Asta the Unworthy will give\Nhis all on this mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:15.94,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle, you're also going with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:16.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:18.96,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Everything counts as experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:21.23,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:23.86,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:26.19,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving those two to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:27.19,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:28.11,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:30.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You'll lose your touch if you \Nstay cooped up all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:31.94,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:36.44,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. Make sure you \Nlook after the newbies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:38.27,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:43.97,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go, too. I wish \Nthey'd take me with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:50.93,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:53.64,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! Lady Noe! Give it your all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:54.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:55.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:10:00.28,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll go find some cute girls, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.43,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:03.76,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,May I go see my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:06.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If you're prepared to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:16.82,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The sunset is beautiful from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:20.09,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I recommend this location for dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:22.91,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have some nummies ready \Nfor you when you get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.44,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:26.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:27.58,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:32.56,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... It's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:40.87,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,They could've just dropped us off \Nright in front of the dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:46.10,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Finral's only able to go to \Nplaces he's been to before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:51.57,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,But thankfully, it was \Nstill near the dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:10.14,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:13.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:19.88,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how the Wizard \NKing even knew about Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:22.63,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:29.46,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,is able to see things we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:31.64,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He's also a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:38.16,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's so dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:41.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cling to me. It's hard to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:43.45,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who's clinging?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:50.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:55.19,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.97,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, could you not step on my foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:12:00.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it! It's pitch black in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being so pissy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:05.11,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because you broke the lamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:06.98,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you have some nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:09.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for tripping \Nand running into me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:12.13,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you? I'm royalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:13.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.39,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:17.65,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:11.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's going on with this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:15.31,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:18.16,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the space is \Nwarped because of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:23.71,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,There's even stronger mana floating \Naround here than outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:28.16,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I've never been anywhere \Nthis full of mana before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:30.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:34.41,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you can't feel all this mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:40.23,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing. I guess people who don't \Nhave magic really are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:42.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:46.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I want to feel mana, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:48.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I want mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice being one of you royals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:52.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You have a ridiculous amount of mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:56.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,In my body, I don't have even an ounce
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:59.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,of the foundation of magic... Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:03.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,God damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.80,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,T-Trap magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:23.76,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That was dangerous. Be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:28.32,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:29.82,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:32.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:33.64,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:45.92,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:47.73,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:49.59,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:50.97,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:04.07,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:09.19,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,And another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:18.33,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,This is so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:20.83,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:24.83,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to die if we stay with this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:29.33,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if those kids are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:35.55,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The more dangerous the mission, the more \Nnewbies will surpass their limits and grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:36.94,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:38.50,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}think{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:41.35,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Luck's with them, \Nso they should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:47.54,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,His ability to detect mana is off the charts.\NIt's even greater than a noble's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:52.98,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If his personality wasn't so messed up, \Nany other squad would've taken him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:57.99,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's that personality \Nwe're worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:59.63,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:06.71,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Man... Your anti-magic weapon is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:10.00,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that's why the \NWizard King chose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:13.20,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to fight you for real \Nin about two to three years!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:18.05,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,If you're prepared to keep swinging \Nyour sword around like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:20.02,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,this dungeon won't be any problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:20.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:23.75,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:28.02,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm about to reach my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:43.38,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:45.75,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,There are others here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:49.44,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest looking one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:54.55,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Creation Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:58.47,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Lightning Boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:02.47,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Something important just came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:07.06,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm leaving the dungeon \Nexploration to you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:09.76,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:13.82,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What in the world is he thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:17.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,S-So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.16,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This is insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:28.11,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Left turn next...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:31.10,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see how \Nstrong this person is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:38.65,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... He's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:43.85,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami clearly told him to \Nkeep an eye on us, and he just left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:46.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:50.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind of traps might spring up,\NI'll slice through them with my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:53.44,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice being as carefree as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:57.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This dungeon ain't nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:18:00.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become the \NWizard King, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:02.40,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Again with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:06.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the Wizard King before Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.34,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:10.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I haven't told you about him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:13.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's a childhood friend\NI grew up with in Hage Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:16.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We took the Magic Knights \NEntrance Exam together,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:19.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and he got into the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:22.79,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:25.56,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He got into the Golden Dawn \Nwithout being a noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:28.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:30.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not gonna lose to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:36.99,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I guess even he has his own goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:38.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:42.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we can cross over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:44.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:48.16,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,We're alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:52.67,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Silvantus... I mean, Nero's with us, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:58.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:02.35,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing! Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:05.22,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.24,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A trap! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:14.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:26.53,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,S-Such powerful magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:37.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:44.38,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:46.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:56.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:22.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:26.35,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Such precise and powerful magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:28.97,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:32.24,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:38.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, a few from the Golden Dawn \Nhave also been assigned to that dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:40.73,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The Golden Dawn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:45.28,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they'll be able to get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:55.75,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:00.42,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I've repaid my debt,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.42,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:04.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:30.74,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My dry emotions gaze at the me from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:33.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And push me forward
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:35.75,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I can't find a place to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:41.03,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the faintest light can \Nstill break through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:46.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And change the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:48.95,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I will keep believing in you)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:51.83,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ever-vivid place
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:54.76,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Break free yourself)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:57.67,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to grasp my endless dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:22:00.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a path that I should choose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.33,0:22:02.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Do you wanna try? Do you wanna try?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.39,0:22:05.30,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever it may lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:07.79,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until my life comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:10.47,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept any pain that comes my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:12.49,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(We can try again, we can try again)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:16.85,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't see tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:22.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding onto feelings too intense to voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.96,0:22:26.13,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep screaming them in my heart
