Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:40.95,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:44.98,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,What's Mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:44.98,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What's Mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:48.54,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, do you know what mana is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.54,0:22:49.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.99,0:22:51.28,sign_32916_371_Mana,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(355,1)}Mana
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:51.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's written like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.28,0:22:53.49,sign_32971_372_Mana,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Mana
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:53.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's written with the same \Ncharacter for "magic"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.49,0:22:55.72,sign_33024_375_Serious_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,244)}Serious
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.02,0:22:56.33,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,These both mean "serious"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.33,0:23:01.96,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Mana is a powerful energy \Nthat exists in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:05.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! And everyone has it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.34,0:23:07.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Except me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:12.59,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Mages use up their mana to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.59,0:23:14.57,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's why if they run out of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.57,0:23:17.60,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,they might not be able to use \Nmagic again until they recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.01,0:23:19.10,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.10,0:23:20.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.35,0:23:25.16,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What a lovely flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:28.44,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect for giving to a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.44,0:23:29.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.82,0:23:32.14,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're so aggressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:34.02,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I've never met a flower like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:38.58,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You've got really powerful magic, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.04,0:23:42.54,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight with everything \Nwe have, to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.54,0:23:47.05,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 15:\N"The Diamond Mage."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.83,0:23:51.39,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 15\N\N{\fs18}The Diamond Mage
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.05,0:23:49.88,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is my magic.
